{"tid":1982442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果㩒個制就可以令香港獨立，你㩒定唔㩒？","createTime":"2020-04-21T08:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T13:27:38.000Z","uid":321421,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57d87c347defc8a687223dd6d84a1c12af45c563","tid":1982442,"uid":321421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"大家成日話簽聯署冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但問心嗰句大家為香港做過啲咩？<br />\n反送中大家都唔肯定自己行出街係咪真係有用<br />\n但就係因為抱住嗰一種「乜都做左先」嘅精神<br />\n所以先有2,000,000+1嘅壯舉<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人同我一樣都好懷念六月嗰一團火<br />\n但與其去回想不如重新燃起鬥志<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 廢憲建國:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DFEOyf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DFEOyf.png&h=0de3db2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsupport-hong-kong-independence&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=900ec365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence</a><br />\n<br />\n最後一日同我推爆佢好冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a30da38f41f979b7497133dba377d2a2d0f746","tid":1982442,"uid":285350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"5c5bb543876684da7691ba7949ee7da5d0f3fd9f","tid":1982442,"uid":129707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:13:52.000Z","msg":"推 點解咁少人簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2f25b279576130e69079b3a38473842204d8f7","tid":1982442,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0a70d5ac886067f5d8cf981dacbc2e7dc33ceb6d","tid":1982442,"uid":